---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Venue & Getting Here"
  description="Both days of EoES 2027 are held in central Norwich. Travel info — train, car, bus, bike."
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="bg-year" aria-hidden="true">NR</div>
  <span class="spark" style="top: 22%; left: 7%;"></span>
  <span class="spark sm" style="top: 60%; right: 12%;"></span>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow"><div class="chip chip--cyan"><span class="dot"></span><span>Venue · Norwich · 2027</span></div></div>
    <h1 class="display-1 hero-title" style="max-width: 16ch;">Norwich.<br><span class="display-italic">Heart of the East.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Both days will be hosted at venues in central Norwich, walking distance from Norwich railway station. Specific venues for 2027 will be confirmed and announced soon.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-2">
      <article class="card" style="border-color: rgba(251,191,36,0.3); padding: 0; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(251,191,36,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);">
        <div style="padding: 22px 28px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-2);">
          <div class="mono" style="color: var(--yellow); margin-bottom: 6px;">— Day 01 · Friday 30 April 2027 —</div>
          <h2 class="h2" style="font-size: 28px;">Workshop Day.</h2>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 28px;">
          <div class="stack-4">
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start;">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="color: var(--yellow); flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M17.66 16.66L13.41 20.9a2 2 0 01-2.83 0l-4.24-4.24a8 8 0 1111.31 0zM15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              <div>
                <div style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 18px; color: var(--ink-0); letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Norwich — venue TBA</div>
                <div class="muted" style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;">Central Norwich. Final venue announced alongside workshop tickets.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: center;">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="color: var(--yellow); flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              <div class="muted">09:00 — 16:30</div>
            </div>
            <p class="muted" style="margin: 0;">A professional conference centre in central Norwich, a short walk from Norwich railway station. Specific location to be confirmed when workshop tickets go on sale.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="card" style="border-color: rgba(236,72,153,0.3); padding: 0; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(236,72,153,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);">
        <div style="padding: 22px 28px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-2);">
          <div class="mono" style="color: var(--pink); margin-bottom: 6px;">— Day 02 · Saturday 1 May 2027 —</div>
          <h2 class="h2" style="font-size: 28px;">Conference Day.</h2>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 28px;">
          <div class="stack-4">
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start;">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="color: var(--pink); flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M17.66 16.66L13.41 20.9a2 2 0 01-2.83 0l-4.24-4.24a8 8 0 1111.31 0zM15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              <div>
                <div style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 18px; color: var(--ink-0); letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Norwich — venue TBA</div>
                <div class="muted" style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;">Central Norwich, fully accessible, well-served by public transport.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: center;">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="color: var(--pink); flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              <div class="muted">08:00 — 17:30</div>
            </div>
            <p class="muted" style="margin: 0;">Specific location to be confirmed and announced via LinkedIn alongside the keynote reveal.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--tight">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head section-head--center">
      <div class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">— Getting Here —</div>
      <h2 class="display-3">Easy to reach<br><span class="display-italic">from across the East.</span></h2>
      <p class="sub">Norwich is easy to reach by train, bus, car or bike.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-2">
      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-icon yellow">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M8 7h8M8 11h8M6 3h12a2 2 0 012 2v12a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2zM9 19v2m6-2v2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="card-title">By train</h3>
        <p class="card-body">Norwich Railway Station is well connected to London Liverpool Street (under 2 hours), Cambridge, Ely and other regional hubs. The venue area is a 5–10 minute walk from the station.</p>
        <p class="muted" style="margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px;">Greater Anglia operates most services. Book in advance for best fares.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-icon pink">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 17a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM19 17a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M13 16V6a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a1 1 0 00-1 1v10l2-1h7l1 1zM13 6h4l4 5v5h-4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="card-title">By car</h3>
        <p class="card-body">Norwich is accessible via the A11 from Cambridge and London, the A47 from the Midlands, and the A140 from Ipswich.</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 14px; padding: 14px; background: rgba(251,191,36,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(251,191,36,0.25); border-radius: 10px;">
          <div class="mono" style="color: var(--yellow); margin-bottom: 6px;">Recommended Parking</div>
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-display); color: var(--ink-0); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Rose Lane Car Park</div>
          <div class="muted" style="font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px;">£8.70/day — significantly cheaper than nearby options.</div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-icon cyan">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M8 6v12M3 12h18M3 6h18a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2H3a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="card-title">By bus</h3>
        <p class="card-body">Norwich has a comprehensive bus network. The bus station on Queen's Road is near the railway station, and the city centre is served by multiple routes.</p>
        <p class="muted" style="margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px;">First Eastern Counties and Konectbus operate most services.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-icon purple">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 6v1m0 0l-3 7m3-7l3 7m-6.5 0a3.5 3.5 0 100 7 3.5 3.5 0 000-7zm9 0a3.5 3.5 0 100 7 3.5 3.5 0 000-7z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="card-title">By bike</h3>
        <p class="card-body">Norwich is bike-friendly with cycle paths and routes into the centre. The city centre has cycle parking and Greater Anglia allows cycles on board when reserved.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--tight">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="frame-panel" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; gap: 28px; align-items: center; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <div class="card-icon yellow" style="margin: 0; width: 56px; height: 56px;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="h3" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Accessibility</h3>
        <p class="muted" style="margin: 0;">Our venues are step-free accessible. If you have specific accessibility requirements, please <a href="/contact" style="color: var(--yellow);">get in touch</a> and we will do everything we can to make your visit comfortable.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
